{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUy_0022","text":"何必妒忌 難道你","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["嫉妒","質疑","不解"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["妒忌","難道"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,4,2,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","bit1","dou3","gei6","naan4","dou6","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"何必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"妒忌","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"難道","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"'何必妒忌 難道你'，語氣帶有質疑和不解，暗示對方不應嫉妒，並引出下一句的解釋。"},"source":{"title":"給愛麗斯","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_252","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUy_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MjUy_0023","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
